ğŸ§­ Introduction to PayCraft

PayCraft is a developer-first fintech platform designed to simplify payments across Africa. It empowers businesses and developers with seamless APIs, intuitive dashboards, and local-first infrastructure to accept, manage, and optimize payments.

ğŸš€ Getting Started with PayCraft

Step 1: Sign Up

