Step 2: Verify Your Account

Submit required documents (business registration, ID, etc.).

Once verified, access your dashboard and API keys.

Step 3: Choose Your Integration Path

No-code: Use PayCraftâ€™s hosted checkout and payment links.

Low-code: Embed widgets into your site.

Full-code: Integrate via RESTful APIs or SDKs.

